description:
We've decided to take a slow start to this new decade and focus on bringing you a solid and well-crafted event for February (details TBA soon). So for January, we're gonna take the opportunity to focus on the networking and friendship aspect of the group and meet for a little social.

Dry January members will be supported!! Also as usual for SWmobile social events please source your own food and we'll cover the beverages.
title: January SWmobile Social
